{"tid":1645907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議：五大訴求升級！","createTime":"2019-10-11T05:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T09:14:56.000Z","uid":296193,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"013517f2f29f285add94cb7f458b0ae2522de42d","tid":1645907,"uid":296193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"抗爭第四個月，政府無道升級，警察暴力升級，訴求升級我覺得合理。既然我地有新口號，訴求都應該更新。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撤回惡法</span></strong><br />\n本來送中法撤回了，偏偏林鄭又出來用緊急法，推蒙面法，此訴求正式歸位！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">解散警隊，成立「永久」獨立調查「機構」</span></strong><br />\n不要「沿水式」調查委員會，要有法定獨立機構制衡紀律部隊執法，追究個別警察，清算罪行<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收回暴動定義</span></strong><br />\n及追究林鄭胡亂使用緊急法之法理依據，林鄭需為此下台及承擔法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">釋放被捕市民、抗爭者並且撤銷控罪</span></strong><br />\n並要求人道對待所有被捕者、關押及在囚人士，追究不人道對待被捕者之警員<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推行雙普選</span></strong><br />\n唯有改革制度，落實民主，才可以永久解決所有深層次問題<br />\n<br />\n其實都係原先五大訴求的延伸，升級，而不是新訴求。大家繼續努力！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"360679b9811d0737d7d80c56f5c91e374ece27db","tid":1645907,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"班狗咁癲係因為冇軍隊制衡<br />\n老解基本上係香港形同虛設 未到最後關頭唔會出"},{"pid":"50bd31f3a45c9c6105c51964b52a7977bf8ad1e2","tid":1645907,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"f3de8d471f050ca88f66c12fcc19cec5be3bdd8e","tid":1645907,"uid":24296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"846b0f843a95b7357eb8fb8c7230d58f205b7bc5","tid":1645907,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"建議廢除暴動罪"},{"pid":"ba8afe53bc7d6b63991dd90d0c91f752ffa93494","tid":1645907,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"一早應該要"},{"pid":"e4ed0dfc05b92916e80c98a2d0aec8b067b525da","tid":1645907,"uid":134342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"真, 惡法唔止送中, 而家仲有緊急法"},{"pid":"b2b934c71e99d6509f71afadfdbbcb202aafafb8","tid":1645907,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"認同"}]}